model_specification: proposed_perc = (trial_role - 1) * (gamma + delta * (token_opp / (token_self + token_opp)) + theta * (trial_type - 2) + kappa * log(combined_earning))
model_summary: A fairness-based proposer model that predicts the percentage of the pot allocated to the opponent. The model integrates the relative token contributions, a trial type adjustment centered on equal contribution, and the scale of combined earnings (via a logarithmic transformation) when the participant acts as a proposer.
